{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"One day a one-eyed monkey came into the forest."},{"time":4000,"text":"Under a tree she saw a woman"},{"time":6000,"text":"meditating furiously."},{"time":9000,"text":"The one-eyed monkey recognized the woman, a Sekhri."},{"time":14000,"text":"She was the wife of an even more famous Brahmin."},{"time":20000,"text":"To watch her better, the one-eyed monkey climbed onto the tree."},{"time":26000,"text":"Just then, with a loud bang,"},{"time":28000,"text":"the heavens opened. (Claps)"},{"time":31000,"text":"And the god Indra jumped into the clearing."},{"time":35000,"text":"Indra saw the woman, a Sekhri."},{"time":37000,"text":"Ah-hah."},{"time":39000,"text":"The woman paid him no heed."},{"time":42000,"text":"So, Indra, attracted, threw her onto the floor,"},{"time":44000,"text":"and proceeded to rape her."},{"time":51000,"text":"Then Indra disappeared. (Clap! Clap!)"},{"time":55000,"text":"And the woman's husband, the Brahmin, appeared."},{"time":61000,"text":"He realized at once what had happened."},{"time":63000,"text":"So, he petitioned the higher gods"},{"time":65000,"text":"so that he may have justice."},{"time":69000,"text":"So, the god Vishnu arrived."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74000,"text":"\"Are there any witnesses?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":77000,"text":"\"Just a one-eyed monkey,\" said the Brahmin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79000,"text":"Now, the one-eyed monkey"},{"time":81000,"text":"really wanted for the woman, a Sekhri, to get justice,"},{"time":85000,"text":"so she retold events exactly as they had happened."},{"time":96000,"text":"Vishnu gave his judgment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99000,"text":"\"The god Indra has sinned,"},{"time":101000,"text":"in that he has sinned against ... a Brahmin."},{"time":105000,"text":"May he be called to wash away his sins.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":109000,"text":"So, Indra arrived,"},{"time":111000,"text":"and performed the sacrifice of the horse."},{"time":114000,"text":"And so it transpired"},{"time":116000,"text":"that a horse was killed,"},{"time":118000,"text":"a god was made sin-free,"},{"time":122000,"text":"a Brahmin's ego was appeased,"},{"time":125000,"text":"a woman ... was ruined,"},{"time":128000,"text":"and a one-eyed monkey was left ..."},{"time":137000,"text":"very confused at what we humans call justice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":143000,"text":"In India there is a rape every three minutes."},{"time":148000,"text":"In India, only 25 percent of rapes"},{"time":153000,"text":"come to a police station,"},{"time":155000,"text":"and of these 25 percent that come to a police station,"},{"time":160000,"text":"convictions are only in four percent of the cases."},{"time":164000,"text":"That's a lot of women who don't get justice."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167000,"text":"And it's not only about women."},{"time":169000,"text":"Look around you, look at your own countries."},{"time":172000,"text":"There is a certain pattern in who gets charged with crimes."},{"time":177000,"text":"If you're in Australia, it's mostly aboriginals who are in jail."},{"time":182000,"text":"If you're in India, it's either Muslims or Adivasis,"},{"time":185000,"text":"our tribals, the Naxalites."},{"time":187000,"text":"If you're in the U.S., it's mostly the blacks."},{"time":192000,"text":"There is a trend here."},{"time":194000,"text":"And the Brahmins and the gods, like in my story,"},{"time":197000,"text":"always get to tell their truth as The Truth."},{"time":200000,"text":"So, have we all become"},{"time":203000,"text":"one-eyed -- two-eyed instead of one-eyed -- monkeys?"},{"time":206000,"text":"Have we stopped seeing injustice?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":210000,"text":"Good morning."},{"time":213000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":217000,"text":"You know, I have told this story"},{"time":222000,"text":"close to 550 times,"},{"time":224000,"text":"in audiences in 40 countries,"},{"time":226000,"text":"to school students, to black-tie dinners at the Smithsonian, and so on and so forth,"},{"time":231000,"text":"and every time it hits something."},{"time":233000,"text":"Now, if I were to go into the same crowd"},{"time":235000,"text":"and say, \"I want to lecture you about justice and injustice,\""},{"time":238000,"text":"they would say, \"Thank you very much, we have other things to do.\""},{"time":241000,"text":"And that is the astonishing power of art."}]},{"cues":[{"time":245000,"text":"Art can go through where other things can't."},{"time":248000,"text":"You can't have barriers, because it breaks through your prejudices,"},{"time":252000,"text":"breaks through everything that you have as your mask,"},{"time":255000,"text":"that says, \"I am this, I am that, I am that.\""},{"time":258000,"text":"No. It breaks through those."},{"time":260000,"text":"And it reaches somewhere where other things don't."},{"time":262000,"text":"And in a world where attitudes are so difficult to change,"},{"time":265000,"text":"we need a language that reaches through."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270000,"text":"Hitler knew it; he used Wagner"},{"time":272000,"text":"to make all the Nazis feel wonderful and Aryan."},{"time":276000,"text":"And Mr. Berlusconi knows it, as he sits atop"},{"time":278000,"text":"this huge empire of media and television and so on and so forth."},{"time":282000,"text":"And all of the wonderful creative minds who are in all the advertising agencies,"},{"time":286000,"text":"and who help corporate sell us things we absolutely don't require,"},{"time":290000,"text":"they also know the power of the arts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":293000,"text":"For me it came very early."},{"time":296000,"text":"When I was a young child, my mother, who was a choreographer,"},{"time":298000,"text":"came upon a phenomenon that worried her."},{"time":301000,"text":"It was a phenomenon where young brides"},{"time":303000,"text":"were committing suicide in rural Gujarat,"},{"time":305000,"text":"because they were being forced to bring more and more money for their in-laws' families."},{"time":310000,"text":"And she created a dance piece which then Prime Minister Nehru saw."},{"time":314000,"text":"He came to talk to her and said, \"What is this about?\""},{"time":316000,"text":"She told him and he set out the first inquiry"},{"time":320000,"text":"into what today we call Dowry Dance."},{"time":323000,"text":"Imagine a dance piece"},{"time":325000,"text":"for the first inquiry into something"},{"time":327000,"text":"that even today kills thousands of women."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332000,"text":"Many years later, when I was working with the director Peter Brook"},{"time":335000,"text":"in \"The Mahabharata\" playing this feisty feminine feminist"},{"time":339000,"text":"called Draupadi, I had similar experiences."},{"time":342000,"text":"Big fat black mamas in the Bronx"},{"time":344000,"text":"used to come and say, \"Hey girl, that's it!\""},{"time":347000,"text":"And then these trendy young things in the Sorbonne would say,"},{"time":349000,"text":"\"Madame Draupadi, on n'est pas feministe, mais ça? Ça!\""},{"time":354000,"text":"And then aboriginal women in Africa"},{"time":356000,"text":"would come and say, \"This is it!\""},{"time":360000,"text":"And I thought, \"This is what we need,"},{"time":363000,"text":"as a language.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":366000,"text":"We had somebody from public health. And Devdutt also mentioned public health."},{"time":370000,"text":"Well, millions of people around the world die"},{"time":373000,"text":"of waterborne disease every year."},{"time":375000,"text":"And that's because there is no clean water to drink,"},{"time":378000,"text":"or in countries like India,"},{"time":380000,"text":"people don't know that they need to soap their hands before defecation."},{"time":383000,"text":"So, what do they do?"},{"time":385000,"text":"They drink the water they know is dirty,"},{"time":387000,"text":"they get cholera, they get diarrhea, they get jaundice"},{"time":390000,"text":"and they die."},{"time":392000,"text":"And governments have not been able to provide clean water."},{"time":397000,"text":"They try and build it. They try and build pipelines; it doesn't happen."},{"time":400000,"text":"And the MNCs give them machines that they cannot afford."},{"time":404000,"text":"So what do you do? Do you let them die?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":406000,"text":"Well, somebody had a great idea."},{"time":408000,"text":"And it was a simple idea. It was an idea that could not profit anybody"},{"time":411000,"text":"but would help health in every field."},{"time":415000,"text":"Most houses in Asia and India"},{"time":417000,"text":"have a cotton garment."},{"time":419000,"text":"And it was discovered, and WHO endorses this,"},{"time":423000,"text":"that a clean cotton garment folded eight times over,"},{"time":426000,"text":"can reduce bacteria up to 80 percent from water sieved through."},{"time":430000,"text":"So, why aren't governments blaring this on television?"},{"time":434000,"text":"Why isn't it on every poster across the third world?"},{"time":438000,"text":"Because there is no profit in it."},{"time":440000,"text":"Because nobody can get a kickback."},{"time":442000,"text":"But it still needs to get to people."},{"time":444000,"text":"And here is one of the ways we get it to people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":446000,"text":"[Video] Woman: Then get me one of those fancy water purifiers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":449000,"text":"Man: You know how expensive those are."},{"time":452000,"text":"I have a solution that requires neither machine,"},{"time":456000,"text":"nor wood, nor cooking gas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":462000,"text":"Woman: What solution?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":464000,"text":"Man: Listen, go fetch that cotton sari you have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":467000,"text":"Boy: Grand-dad, tell me the solution please."}]},{"cues":[{"time":469000,"text":"Man: I will tell all of you. Just wait."}]},{"cues":[{"time":471000,"text":"Woman: Here father. (Man: Is it clean?) Woman: Yes, of course."}]},{"cues":[{"time":474000,"text":"Man: Then do as I tell you. Fold the sari into eight folds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":477000,"text":"Woman: All right, father."}]},{"cues":[{"time":479000,"text":"Man: And you, you count that she does it right. (Boy: All right, grand-dad.)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":482000,"text":"Man: One, two, three, four folds we make."},{"time":484000,"text":"All the germs from the water we take."}]},{"cues":[{"time":487000,"text":"Chorus: One, two, three, four folds we make."},{"time":489000,"text":"All the germs from the water we take."},{"time":492000,"text":"Five, six, seven, eight folds we make."},{"time":494000,"text":"Our drinking water safe we make."},{"time":497000,"text":"Five, six, seven, eight folds we make."},{"time":499000,"text":"Our drinking water safe we make."}]},{"cues":[{"time":502000,"text":"Woman: Here, father, your eight-times folded cotton sari."}]},{"cues":[{"time":504000,"text":"Man: So this is the cotton sari."},{"time":507000,"text":"And through this we will have clean water."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":514000,"text":"I think it's safe to say that all of us here"},{"time":516000,"text":"are deeply concerned about the escalating violence in our daily lives."},{"time":521000,"text":"While universities are trying to devise courses in conflict resolution,"},{"time":524000,"text":"and governments are trying to stop skirmishes at borders,"},{"time":528000,"text":"we are surrounded by violence, whether it's road rage,"},{"time":531000,"text":"or whether it's domestic violence,"},{"time":533000,"text":"whether it's a teacher beating up a student and killing her"},{"time":537000,"text":"because she hasn't done her homework, it's everywhere."},{"time":540000,"text":"So, why are we not doing something"},{"time":542000,"text":"to actually attend that problem on a day to day basis?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":544000,"text":"What are we doing to try and make children"},{"time":547000,"text":"and young people realize"},{"time":549000,"text":"that violence is something that we indulge in,"},{"time":552000,"text":"that we can stop,"},{"time":554000,"text":"and that there are other ways of actually"},{"time":556000,"text":"taking violence, taking anger, taking frustrations"},{"time":560000,"text":"into different things that do not harm other people."},{"time":563000,"text":"Well, here is one such way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566000,"text":"(Video) (Laughs) You are peaceful people."},{"time":571000,"text":"Your parents were peaceful people."},{"time":575000,"text":"Your grandparents were peaceful people."},{"time":579000,"text":"So much peace in one place?"},{"time":583000,"text":"How could it be otherwise?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":586000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":590000,"text":"But, what if ..."},{"time":595000,"text":"Yes. What if ..."},{"time":600000,"text":"One little gene in you"},{"time":602000,"text":"has been trying to get through?"},{"time":605000,"text":"From your beginnings in Africa,"},{"time":607000,"text":"through each generation, may be passed on to you,"},{"time":610000,"text":"in your creation. It's a secret urge, hiding deep in you."},{"time":614000,"text":"And if it's in you, then it's in me too. Oh, dear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":620000,"text":"It's what made you smack your baby brother,"},{"time":624000,"text":"stamp on a cockroach, scratch your mother."},{"time":627000,"text":"It's the feeling that wells up from deep inside,"},{"time":630000,"text":"when your husband comes home drunk and you wanna tan his hide."},{"time":635000,"text":"Want to kill that cyclist on the way to work,"},{"time":638000,"text":"and string up your cousin 'cause she's such a jerk. Oh, dear."},{"time":645000,"text":"And as for outsiders, white, black or brown,"},{"time":648000,"text":"tar and feather them, and whip them out of town."}]},{"cues":[{"time":651000,"text":"It's that little gene. It's small and it's mean."},{"time":654000,"text":"Too small for detection, it's your built-in protection."},{"time":658000,"text":"Adrenaline, kill. It'll give you the will."},{"time":661000,"text":"Yes, you'd better face it 'cause you can't displace it."},{"time":664000,"text":"You're V-I-O-L-E-N-T."},{"time":667000,"text":"Cause you're either a victim, or on top, like me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":687000,"text":"Goodbye, Abraham Lincoln."},{"time":692000,"text":"Goodbye, Mahatma Gandhi."},{"time":696000,"text":"Goodbye, Martin Luther King."},{"time":700000,"text":"Hello, gangs from this neighborhood"},{"time":704000,"text":"killing gangs from that neighborhood."},{"time":708000,"text":"Hello governments of rich countries"},{"time":711000,"text":"selling arms to governments of poor countries"},{"time":715000,"text":"who can't even afford to give them food."},{"time":719000,"text":"Hello civilization. Hello, 21st century."},{"time":724000,"text":"Look what we've ..."},{"time":729000,"text":"look what they've done."},{"time":734000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":740000,"text":"Mainstream art, cinema,"},{"time":743000,"text":"has been used across the world to talk about social issues."},{"time":747000,"text":"A few years ago we had a film called Rang De Basanti,"},{"time":750000,"text":"which suddenly spawned thousands of young people"},{"time":754000,"text":"wanting to volunteer for social change."},{"time":756000,"text":"In Venezuela, one of the most popular"},{"time":758000,"text":"soap operas has a heroine called Crystal."},{"time":760000,"text":"And when, onscreen, Crystal got breast cancer,"},{"time":764000,"text":"75,000 more young women went to have mammographies done."},{"time":770000,"text":"And of course, \"The Vagina Monologues\" we know about."},{"time":772000,"text":"And there are stand-up comics"},{"time":774000,"text":"who are talking about racial issues, about ethnic issues."}]},{"cues":[{"time":777000,"text":"So, why is it,"},{"time":779000,"text":"that if we think that we all agree"},{"time":782000,"text":"that we need a better world,"},{"time":784000,"text":"we need a more just world,"},{"time":786000,"text":"why is it that we are not using the one language"},{"time":788000,"text":"that has consistently showed us"},{"time":790000,"text":"that we can break down barriers, that we can reach people?"},{"time":794000,"text":"What I need to say to the planners of the world,"},{"time":797000,"text":"the governments, the strategists"},{"time":799000,"text":"is, \"You have treated the arts as the cherry on the cake."},{"time":804000,"text":"It needs to be the yeast.\""},{"time":806000,"text":"Because, any future planning,"},{"time":809000,"text":"if 2048 is when we want to get there,"},{"time":812000,"text":"unless the arts are put with the scientists,"},{"time":815000,"text":"with the economists,"},{"time":817000,"text":"with all those who prepare for the future, badly,"},{"time":822000,"text":"we're not going to get there."},{"time":825000,"text":"And unless this is actually internalized, it won't happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":829000,"text":"So, what is it that we require? What is it that we need?"},{"time":832000,"text":"We need to break down our vision"},{"time":835000,"text":"of what planners are,"},{"time":837000,"text":"of what the correct way of a path is."},{"time":840000,"text":"And to say all these years of trying"},{"time":842000,"text":"to make a better world, and we have failed."},{"time":844000,"text":"There are more people being raped. There are more wars."},{"time":847000,"text":"There are more people dying of simple things."},{"time":850000,"text":"So, something has got to give. And that is what I want."},{"time":853000,"text":"Can I have my last audio track please?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":858000,"text":"Once there was a princess who whistled beautifully."},{"time":862000,"text":"(Whistling)"},{"time":865000,"text":"Her father the king said, \"Don't whistle.\""},{"time":868000,"text":"Her mother the queen said, \"Hai, don't whistle.\""},{"time":871000,"text":"But the princess continued whistling."},{"time":874000,"text":"(Whistling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":878000,"text":"The years went by and the princess grew up"},{"time":880000,"text":"into a beautiful young woman,"},{"time":882000,"text":"who whistled even more beautifully."},{"time":884000,"text":"(Whistling)"},{"time":889000,"text":"Her father the king said, \"Who will marry a whistling princess?\""},{"time":893000,"text":"Her mother the queen said, \"Who will marry a whistling princess?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":897000,"text":"But the king had an idea."},{"time":899000,"text":"He announced a Swayamvara."},{"time":901000,"text":"He invited all the princes to come and defeat his daughter at whistling."},{"time":905000,"text":"\"Whoever defeats my daughter shall have half my kingdom"},{"time":908000,"text":"and her hand in marriage!\""},{"time":911000,"text":"Soon the palace filled with princes whistling."},{"time":916000,"text":"(Whistling)"},{"time":918000,"text":"Some whistled badly."},{"time":921000,"text":"Some whistled well."},{"time":923000,"text":"But nobody could defeat the princess."}]},{"cues":[{"time":927000,"text":"\"Now what shall we do?\" said the king."},{"time":930000,"text":"\"Now what shall we do?\" said the queen."},{"time":932000,"text":"But the princess said, \"Father, Mother, don't worry."},{"time":935000,"text":"I have an idea. I am going to go to each of these young men"},{"time":938000,"text":"and I am going to ask them"},{"time":940000,"text":"if they defeated correctly."},{"time":942000,"text":"And if somebody answers, that shall be my wish.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":945000,"text":"So she went up to each and said, \"Do you accept that I have defeated you?\""},{"time":949000,"text":"And they said, \"Me? Defeated by a woman?"},{"time":951000,"text":"No way, that's impossible! No no no no no! That's not possible.\""},{"time":955000,"text":"Till finally one prince said,"},{"time":957000,"text":"\"Princess, I accept, you have defeated me.\""},{"time":963000,"text":"\"Uh-huh ...\" she said."},{"time":965000,"text":"\"Father, mother, this man shall be my wife.\""},{"time":969000,"text":"(Whistling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":974000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":976000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}